item.title: CVE-2019-6626|2024-08-04T20:23:22.156Z -- f5 -- big-ip%20%28afm%2C%20analytics%2C%20asm%29
item.description: On BIG-IP (AFM, Analytics, ASM) 14.1.0-14.1.0.5, 14.0.0-14.0.0.4, 13.0.0-13.1.1.4, 12.1.0-12.1.4, and 11.5.1-11.6.3.4, A reflected cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exists in an undisclosed page of the BIG-IP Traffic Management User Interface (TMUI), also known as the Configuration utility.
